Class NetDuplexController

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.nolix.nolixCommonLibrary.duplexController.DuplexController
      • ch.nolix.nolixCommonLibrary.duplexController.NetDuplexController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IController, IControlleroid, IDuplexController, Stoppable

    public final class NetDuplexController
extends DuplexController
    A net duplex controller is a duplex controller on an other process. The other process can be -on the same computer -on an other computer which can be reached through a net connection.
